{"words":[{"word":"fractsidus","count":2},{"word":"site","count":2},{"word":"dreams","count":2},{"word":"alright","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"probably","count":1},{"word":"things","count":1},{"word":"figured","count":1},{"word":"calls","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"ran","count":1},{"word":"experiments","count":1},{"word":"photonvault","count":1},{"word":"created","count":1},{"word":"court","count":1},{"word":"savantae","count":1},{"word":"frozen","count":1},{"word":"animals","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"device's","count":1},{"word":"test","count":1},{"word":"subjects","count":1},{"word":"caught","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"monsters","count":1},{"word":"loong's","count":1},{"word":"crest","count":1},{"word":"must've","count":1},{"word":"captured","count":1},{"word":"plan","count":1},{"word":"memo","count":1},{"word":"mentioned","count":1},{"word":"frequency","count":1},{"word":"suppressor","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1},{"word":"control","count":1},{"word":"diary","count":1},{"word":"absurd","count":1},{"word":"mad","count":1},{"word":"power","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"worth","count":1},{"word":"doubt","count":1},{"word":"killers","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"cities","count":1},{"word":"jinzhou","count":1},{"word":"hongzhen","count":1},{"word":"offer","count":1},{"word":"protection","count":1},{"word":"folks","count":1},{"word":"daily","count":1},{"word":"lives","count":1},{"word":"looking","count":1},{"word":"kind","count":1},{"word":"trouble","count":1},{"word":"wrap","count":1},{"word":"head","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"excuse","count":1},{"word":"stop","count":1},{"word":"away","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Alright, I think I've probably got things figured out.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"The Fractsidus calls this place \"Site 2\" and ran experiments with the \"Photonvault\" created by the Court of Savantae.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Those frozen animals? They must be the device's test subjects caught in time.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"And the monsters at Loong's Crest must've been captured with it, too.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"But what's their plan? The memo from Site 1 mentioned a frequency suppressor… What’s that for?","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Yes… So they can control them, like in the diary.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"This is absurd...","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Are they all mad? Why would they do this?","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"For power? Is it really worth all this?","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"For dreams? I doubt these killers know anything about dreams.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"But cities like Jinzhou or Hongzhen offer protection. Folks can go about their daily lives, so why go looking for this kind of trouble?","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"I just... can't wrap my head around it. There's no excuse for this.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"You're right. We have to stop the Fractsidus. We can't let them get away with this.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016}]}